<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0),rgba(0,0,0,0)), url(<%= asset_path 'banner.png' %>);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-orange my-3" style="width: 100px">
      <%= render "shared/logo" %>
    </div>
    <h1 class="fw-bold "><strong>If animals could talk,</strong></h1>
    <h1 class="fw-bold"><strong>they'd talk about <strong style="color: #FD8522">Us</strong></strong></h1>
    <p class="mt-4 mb-5">Join the largest network of pet sitters in Latin America.</p>
    <a class="btn btn-info text-white btn-lg px-5 text-white rounded-pill" href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>">Sign Up</a>
    <a class="btn btn-warning text-white btn-lg px-5 rounded-pill ms-2" href="<%= new_user_session_path %>">Login</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-5 my-5">
      <div class="text-center d-flex flex-column gap-5">
        <h2 class="mt-4">What do you need to be a <span class="fw-bold" style= 'color: #FD8522' >Pet Carer</span>?</h2>
        <div class="row my-2">
          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 shadow-sm mx-0 p-3">
            <i class="fa-regular fa-id-card" style="font-size: 50px; color: #FD8522;"></i>
            <h5 class="m-3"><strong>Be of age</strong></h5>
            <p>You must be at least 18 years old.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 shadow-sm mx-0 p-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-house-user" style="font-size: 50px; color: #FD8522;"></i>
            <h5 class="m-3"><strong>Photos of your space</strong></h5>
            <p>Take photos of your tidy and spacious space.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 shadow-sm mx-0 p-3">
            <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-question" style="font-size: 50px; color: #FD8522;"></i>
            <h5 class="m-3"><strong>Contact information</strong></h5>
            <p>You need an active cell phone where we can communicate.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 shadow-sm mx-0 p-3">
            <i class="fa-regular fa-user" style="font-size: 50px; color: #FD8522;"></i>
            <h5 class="m-3"><strong>Proof of identity</strong></h5>
            <p>It can be your INE, Passport or driver's license.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

       <div class="container my-5">
    <!-- Primera fila: Imagen a la izquierda, texto a la derecha -->
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="border rounded custom-card">
          <img src="<%= asset_path('review2.jpg') %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Imagen 1" style="
    border-radius: 20px !important;">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 p-5">
        <p class="custom-text fs-5 fst-italic mb-5">
         " Being a pet sitter has given me many learnings and also company for both me and my dog. <br> We enjoyed time with the pets and getting to know them as if they were my own for a few days."
        </p>
        <p class="text-info py-2 px-4 fs-6"><span class="fw-bold">Andrea</span > - Mexico City</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Segunda fila: Texto a la izquierda, imagen a la derecha -->
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-2">
        <div class="border rounded custom-card">
          <img src="<%= asset_path('review3.jpg') %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Imagen 2" style="
    border-radius: 20px !important;">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-1 p-5">
        <p class="custom-text fs-5 fst-italic mb-5">
          " Finding the perfect caregiver was a breeze. My dog was well-cared for, and I felt confident knowing he was in good hands. <br> Highly recommend <strong style="color: #FD8522">PetCare</strong> for anyone seeking trustworthy pet sitters."
        </p>
        <p class="text-info py-2 px-4 fs-6"><span class="fw-bold">Juan</span> - Guadalajara</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      <div class="text-center d-flex flex-column gap-5">
        <h2 class="m-0">How does it work?</h2>
        <div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
              <p class="circle-number text-center">1</p>
              <h5 class="mt-3">Review service announcements posted by other users.</h5>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
              <p class="circle-number text-center">2</p>
              <h5 class="mt-3">Choose the pet sitter that best suits your needs.</h5>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
              <p class="circle-number text-center">3</p>
              <h5 class="mt-3">Wait for the sitter to accept the request.</h5>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
              <p class="circle-number text-center">4</p>
              <h5 class="mt-3">Set your pet's calendars</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
   </div>
</div>
